'''Aferẓiẓ''' neɣ '''izirẓeg''' ([[Assaɣ usnnan]]: '''Citrullus colocynthis''') d [[talmest]] n [[imɣan|yimɣan]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawsit (tudersent)|tawsit]] n [[Aferẓiẓ (tawsit)|uferẓiẓ]] igan d yiwet n tewsit seg tewsitin n [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[Tiqlilucin (tawacult)|teqlilucin]]. 

[[Iferr|Iferran-is]] d ikenkaren (d iḥercawen), itessu tagnit anda i d-issufuɣ [[aɣris|iɣrisen]] itezzin ɣef yimɣan yudsen fell-as i wakken ad ṭṭfen s yis. Yettemɣay-d s tuget deg tazwara n [[amwan|umwan]].

